Gretchen Wyler https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretchen_Wyler 0 Gretchen Wyler (born Gretchen Patricia Wienecke; February 16, 1932 – May 27, 2007) was an American actress and dancer. She was also an animal rights advocate and founder of the Genesis Awards for animal protection.
